{"tid":1970140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地工廠復工惟面對困難　學者料中國首季GDP或較差","createTime":"2020-04-13T02:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T05:06:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b03965b438dd955dd648e5375160090ac129a9aa","tid":1970140,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"受武漢肺炎疫情打擊致要封城70多天的武漢，上星期三解封，有市民為生計，戰戰兢兢冒著或會感染病毒風險復工。另外，雖然內地2月中陸續復工，但不少廠家既面對工人不足、訂單大減等種種問題。<br />\n<br />\n廣東一間鞋廠的負責人說，生意減少近7成，即使9成員工已返回崗位，但有一半人要安排停工留職，湖北省員工亦暫時不用回廠。<br />\n<br />\n另一間廣東針織廠的負責人說，當局要求企業向未能上班員工支付基本工資，加上受英國疫情影響，被要求延期出貨到當地，財政因而略受影響。<br />\n<br />\n亦有工廠在復工初期，一度因零部件供應不足影響生產，其後要追回進度，但又面對貨物交收延遲問題。負責人說，工廠接了東京奧運的訂單，但奧運延期一年舉辦，目前要解決貨物積壓等問題。<br />\n<br />\n中大劉佐德全球經濟及金融研究所常務所長莊太量預計，受疫情影響，中國第一季GDP會較差，目前內地8成企業已復工，加上當局加速基建投資，相信經濟未來會有改善。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520334-20200413.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520334-20200413.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=48a60836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520334-20200413.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=886a0011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520334-20200413.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"23d8dd8615282e9702425e19f8a2e6ea67d2b35b","tid":1970140,"uid":106321,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:28:47.000Z","msg":"好快就見到支那人輪住跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216d87b698d00e66655dc8a89f3f5fbb788a5dd4","tid":1970140,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:32:56.000Z","msg":"如果第三波係解做中國再次帶病毒黎香港<br />\n第四波係咪因為會復工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f9d7977de3e41051424d3a141f4b1bf5efa6a4","tid":1970140,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"咁嚴重嘅疫情拖延咁耐 都係較差GDP？<br />\n<br />\n咁全世界真係應該快啲撤廠"},{"pid":"cbe69ecb4aa76c09c7c264cdb20191a93c39dea0","tid":1970140,"uid":204803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:43:25.000Z","msg":"冇單復工黎把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快D支爆死撚哂佢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0aabafac6d14696cb027fc61cd6aee412348116","tid":1970140,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"最後有6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n信我 反正都係假"},{"pid":"cab9fb03a0ab44648b96cb289f0324da7094a574","tid":1970140,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"點都贏啦"},{"pid":"b87c6b3de73f2855e41b8eacd380524ec2b86a8b","tid":1970140,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23d8dd8615282e9702425e19f8a2e6ea67d2b35b","tid":1970140,"uid":106321,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:28:47.000Z","msg":"好快就見到支那人輪住跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"呢一日好快出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}